        "content": "## Phase 2 — LLM Content Generation\nPrimary: Gemini 3 Pro\nFallback: Claude Opus 4.1\nJSON fixer: gpt-5-mini via OpenRouter\n\nOutputs: post_body + image prompts for front / content slides / CTA",
