    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Phase 3 — Image Generation (parallel)\n\nThree branches run from Split Out simultaneously:\n\n● Front (Limit1 → Generate → Upload → Tag [order=0])\n● Content x N (Generate → Upload → Tag [order=$itemIndex+1])\n● CTA (Limit2 → Generate → Upload → Tag [order=9999])\n\ngpt-image-1 creates each slide from scratch — no templates.\nTag nodes stamp type + order before merge.\nCollect & Order sorts: Front → Content → CTA.\n\n✓ → Update Supabase status=completed\n✗ → Update Supabase status=failed",
        "height": 608,
        "width": 1600,
        "color": 7
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        4256,
