      ],
      "id": "c7236f39-74e4-4783-9d82-70e756291d30",
      "name": "Note Phase 3"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## VSS Carousel Creator — Supabase v2\n\n## One-time Setup\n\n### 1. Supabase URL (3 nodes)\nReplace `YOUR_PROJECT_REF` in:\n- `Set Processing Status`\n- `Update Carousel — Completed`\n- `Update Carousel — Failed`\n\nFind it: Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API → Project URL\n\n### 2. Supabase Service Role Key credential\nCredentials → Add → Header Auth\n- Header Name: `apikey`\n- Value: your service_role JWT (starts with eyJ, ~200 chars)\n- Map to all 3 Supabase PATCH nodes above\n- DO NOT use the native Supabase node (403 bug — GitHub #17020)\n\n### 3. OpenAI API Key credential\nCredentials → Add → OpenAI\n- Map to: `Generate Front Slide`, `Generate Content Slide`, `Generate CTA Slide`\n- Required for gpt-image-1 image generation\n\n### 4. ImgBB API Key\nCredentials → Add → Query Auth\n- Parameter name: `key`\n- Value: your ImgBB API key\n- Map to: `Upload Front to ImgBB`, `Upload Content to ImgBB`, `Upload CTA to ImgBB`\n\n### 5. LLM credentials\n- Gemini (primary LLM): map to `Gemini-3-pro` node\n- Anthropic (fallback LLM): map to `Opus-4.1-thinking` node\n- OpenRouter (JSON fixer): map to `gpt-5-mini` node\n\n## Webhook Payload (from Phase 5 /api/generate)\ncarousel_id, idea_text, brand_name, brand_color,\nvoice_guidelines, product_description, audience_description,\ncta_text, style_name, design_style, custom_instructions\n\n## What this workflow does\n1. Responds 202 immediately (caller never waits)\n2. Updates Supabase status → processing\n3. LLM generates post body + image prompts for all slides\n4. gpt-image-1 generates each slide from scratch (no templates needed)\n5. Uploads each slide to ImgBB for permanent hosting\n6. Orders slides: Front → Content (1..N) → CTA\n7. Updates Supabase → completed (with slide_urls + post_body) or failed",
        "height": 620,
        "width": 860
      },
